---
title: Smart Double Shrimp Curry with Buttered Couscous
description: This silky, fragrant curry sauce built with warm spices, tomatoes and cream cheese is sure to delight your palate! A healthy serving of shrimp and a side of light couscous make this meal a wholesome wonder.

